#. <section class="sutta" id="sn4.10"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn4.10:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 4"
msgstr "Linked Discourses 4"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "sn4.10:0.2"
msgid "1. Paṭhamavagga"
msgstr "1. Life Span"

#. </p><h1>
msgctxt "sn4.10:0.3"
msgid "10. Dutiyaāyusutta"
msgstr "10. Life Span (2nd)"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
#. <span class="evam">
msgctxt "sn4.10:1.1"
msgid "Evaṃ me sutaṃ—"
msgstr "So I have heard."

#. </span>
msgctxt "sn4.10:1.2"
msgid "ekaṃ samayaṃ bhagavā rājagahe viharati veḷuvane kalandakanivāpe."
msgstr ""
"At one time the Buddha was staying near Rājagaha, in the Bamboo Grove, the "
"squirrels’ feeding ground."

msgctxt "sn4.10:1.3"
msgid "Tatra kho bhagavā … pe … etadavoca:"
msgstr "There the Buddha … said:"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc2"></a>
msgctxt "sn4.10:2.1"
msgid "“Appamidaṃ, bhikkhave, manussānaṃ āyu."
msgstr "“Mendicants, the life span of humans is short."

msgctxt "sn4.10:2.2"
msgid "Gamanīyo samparāyo, kattabbaṃ kusalaṃ, caritabbaṃ brahmacariyaṃ."
msgstr ""
"You must go to the next life. So you should do what is skillful, you should "
"practice the spiritual life."

msgctxt "sn4.10:2.3"
msgid "Natthi jātassa amaraṇaṃ."
msgstr "No-one born is immortal."

msgctxt "sn4.10:2.4"
msgid "Yo, bhikkhave, ciraṃ jīvati, so vassasataṃ appaṃ vā bhiyyo”ti."
msgstr "A long life is a hundred years or a little more.”"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc3"></a>
msgctxt "sn4.10:3.1"
msgid ""
"Atha kho māro pāpimā yena bhagavā tenupasaṅkami; upasaṅkamitvā bhagavantaṃ "
"gāthāya ajjhabhāsi:"
msgstr "Then Māra the Wicked went up to the Buddha and addressed him in verse:"

#. </p><blockquote class="gatha"><p>
#. <a class="pts1ed" id="pts1ed1.109"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc4"></a>
msgctxt "sn4.10:4.1"
msgid "“Nāccayanti ahorattā,"
msgstr "“The days and nights don’t rush by,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn4.10:4.2"
msgid "Jīvitaṃ nūparujjhati;"
msgstr "and life isn’t cut short."

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn4.10:4.3"
msgid "Āyu anupariyāyati maccānaṃ,"
msgstr "The life of mortals keeps rolling on,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn4.10:4.4"
msgid "Nemīva rathakubbaran”ti."
msgstr "like a chariot’s rim around the hub.”"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="pts2ed" id="pts2ed1.243"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc5"></a>
msgctxt "sn4.10:5.1"
msgid "“Accayanti ahorattā,"
msgstr "“The days and nights rush by,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn4.10:5.2"
msgid "jīvitaṃ uparujjhati;"
msgstr "and then life is cut short."

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn4.10:5.3"
msgid "Āyu khīyati maccānaṃ,"
msgstr "The life of mortals wastes away,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn4.10:5.4"
msgid "kunnadīnaṃva odakan”ti."
msgstr "like the water in tiny streams.”"

#. </p></blockquote><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc6"></a>
msgctxt "sn4.10:6.1"
msgid ""
"Atha kho māro pāpimā “jānāti maṃ bhagavā, jānāti maṃ sugato”ti dukkhī "
"dummano tatthevantaradhāyīti."
msgstr ""
"Then Māra the Wicked, thinking, “The Buddha knows me! The Holy One knows me!”"
" miserable and sad, vanished right there."

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn4.10:6.2"
msgid "Paṭhamo vaggo."
msgstr ""

#. </p><blockquote class="uddanagatha"><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc7"></a>
msgctxt "sn4.10:7.1"
msgid "Tapokammañca nāgo ca,"
msgstr ""

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn4.10:7.2"
msgid "subhaṃ pāsena te duve;"
msgstr ""

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn4.10:7.3"
msgid "Sappo supati nandanaṃ,"
msgstr ""

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn4.10:7.4"
msgid "āyunā apare duveti."
msgstr ""
